Welcome to Open Security Summit 2020 Thank you for your interest in Open Security Summit 2020 (OSS 2020).
The attendee general flow (attendee journey) is as follows;
Buy a ticket Remote participants should also register using EventBrite. Create personal participant page Find sessions that you are interested in by viewing the topic index, tracks view or just simply list working, user or product sessions. Register to attend a session.
